\id 1TI Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular
\mt1 ﾆ、TAKURU PUULUSA ARANURU HAA E TIMOTEE
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Immorde e an min Puulusa, mo Alla, on Danduﾉ熔 en, e Iisaa Almasiihu, on wonﾉ熔 tama'u men, yamiri wonugol *sahaabaajo Iisaa Almasiihu on.
\p 
\v 2 Mi salminii ma yo Timotee, an oo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 an e nder gomﾉ擁nal.
\p Yo Alla Baabaajo on e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on yeﾉ容 moﾆｴﾆｴere e yurmeende e ﾉ砥ttu.
\s1 Fii Reenagol e Jandeeji Fenaandeeji
\p 
\v 3 Wano mi wakkilinirno-maa non wonugol Efeesi ﾉ熔n, fewndo ko mi fokkiti Masedonii, fii yo a yamir woﾉ橡兎 goo wota ﾉ兎 jannu janndeeji goo,
\v 4 e wota ﾉ兎 cato e tindi mehi e lasilankaaku ngu lannataa, ko memminta yeddondire, hara hinaa waﾉ蓉gol golle Alla ﾉ容n e nder gomﾉ擁nal.
\v 5 Ko woni faandaare ndee yamiroore, ko yiﾉ擁rgol ﾉ兎rnde laaﾉ砥nde e fondo moﾆｴﾆｴo e gomﾉ擁nal ngal aldaa e faasiqankaaku.
\v 6 Woﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n sortii e ﾉ容n pehe, ukkii e haalaaji mehi,
\v 7 hara hiﾉ兎 faalaa wonude jannooﾉ兎 fii Sariya on, e hin-le ﾉ兎 faamanaa hay ko ﾉ兎 woni wi'ude kon, e ko ﾉ兎 woni tentinde fii mun kon.
\p 
\v 8 Hiﾉ容n andi tigi wonde Sariya on no moﾆｴﾆｴi, kono ko e hoore jogitorgol mo no haaniri.
\v 9 Awa kadi anden Sariya on waﾉ擁raaka fii feewuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, kono ko fii bonﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e dartiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e junuubankeeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e ﾉ兎 rewataa Alla ﾉ兎n e hayfinooﾉ兎 fii Alla ﾉ兎n e warooﾉ兎 ben mun e yumma mun ﾉ兎n e ittooﾉ兎 ko'e ﾉ兎n
\v 10 e jeenooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e worﾉ兎 jinooﾉ兎 worﾉ兎 e yeeyooﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 e fenooﾉ兎 e woondooﾉ兎 fenaande ﾉ兎n e kala waﾉ熔oﾉ兎 kuuﾉ容 woopondirﾉ容 e jannde haqiiqaare nden.
\v 11 Ndee jannde no yaadi e Kibaaru Moﾆｴﾆｴo mo o halfinimmi on, on ﾉ殿nginﾉ熔 mangural Alla moﾆｴﾆｴo on.
\s1 Fii Moﾆｴﾆｴere nde Alla Yeﾉ擁 Puulusa nden
\p 
\v 12 Mi jarnii on yeﾉ遼擁nﾉ熔 lan, ﾉ蓉n ko Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on, jogitorﾉ熔 lan wa holniiﾉ熔, toﾉ遼擁i mi e ﾉ容e golle makko,
\v 13 min oo hoynaynooﾉ熔, cukkotonooﾉ熔, yennaynooﾉ熔. Kono mi yurminaa, ko fii ko mi wonnoo warrude ﾉ蓉n, ko angal gandal e angal gomﾉ擁nal.
\v 14 Joomiraaﾉ熔 on yeﾉ擁i lan moﾆｴﾆｴere no yaajiri, wondude e gomﾉ擁nal e giggol ko woni e Iisaa Almasiihu on kon.
\v 15 Ngol kongol ﾉ熔o ko haqiiqawol, hingol handi e jaﾉ兎ede few, ngol-le e hino ngol: Iisaa Almasiihu on ko ardi ka aduna ko dandugol junuubanke'en. Min non ko mi ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 bonde e ﾉ兎n.
\v 16 Kono mi yurminaa, fii no Iisaa Almasiihu on ﾉ殿nginira e an, min oo ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 bonde, yondinaare makko nden fow, fii no mi wonira misal e gomﾉ擁noyooﾉ兎 e makko ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 heﾉ殿 *ngurndan poomayankejan.
\v 17 Teddungal e mangu wonanii Lanﾉ熔 poomayankeejo, mo maayataa, mo yi'otaako, Alla bajjo, haa poomaa. Aamiina!
\p 
\v 18 Ndee yamiroore nde mi yamir-maa, yo Timotee ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 an, wano *hiitoraa fii maa non, ko yo a tippir tippiro moﾆｴﾆｴo ngon
\v 19 e nder gomﾉ擁nal wondude e ﾉ兎rnde laaﾉ砥nde. Nden ﾉ兎rnde laaﾉ砥nde non woﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n tertike nde, haa ka tawata gomﾉ擁nal maﾉ橡兎 ngal yoolike.
\v 20 No tawaa e ﾉ兎n Himenee e Aleksander, ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 mi accidi e Ibuliisa fii jannugol ﾉ兎 wota ﾉ兎 hoynu Alla.
\c 2
\s1 Fii Dewal e Toraare Alla
\p 
\v 1 Ko adii kon taho, miﾉ熔 torii yo en landano yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fow ballal Alla, waﾉ預nen ﾉ兎 torndeeji e du'aaji e yettooje Alla,
\v 2 waﾉ預nen ﾉ蓉n kadi lamﾉ兎 e kala yeesooﾉ兎, fii no wuuriren ngurndan newiiﾉ預n e ﾉ砥ttuﾉ預n wano Alla faaliraa non e hoore teddungal.
\v 3 Ko ﾉ蓉n woni ko moﾆｴﾆｴi, ko welata Alla, Danduﾉ熔 en on,
\v 4 on Yiﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 yo yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fow dande, ﾉ兎 ara e andugol goonga on.
\v 5 Ko fii ko Alla gooto woodi, no woodi kadi moﾆｴﾆｴintinoowo gooto hakkunde makko e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ蓉n ko oo neﾉ遼熔 wi'eteeﾉ熔 Iisaa Almasiihu,
\v 6 on sakkiiﾉ熔 hoore mun fii sottugol fow, ﾉ蓉n ko seedee waﾉ預aﾉ熔 e saa'i toﾉ遼預aﾉ熔 on.
\v 7 Ko fii feﾉｲﾉｲingol on seedee waﾉ擁 si mi waﾉ擁raa waajotooﾉ熔 e yottinoowo, (mi wowlay goonga, mi fenataa), fii ko janna ﾉ兎 wonaa Yahuudiyanke ﾉ兎n ko woni gomﾉ擁nal goongawal ngal kon.
\p 
\v 8 Miﾉ熔 yiﾉ擁 kadi yo worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n toro Alla ka woni woo, e hoore townugol juuﾉ容 laaﾉ砥ﾉ容 e ﾉ殿awo tikkere e yeddondiral.
\p 
\v 9 Rewﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kadi wano non, ﾉ兎 ﾉ登rnora no haaniri, hara hinaa no maniree e no hawnori, hara ﾉ兎 ukkaaki e morﾉ擁 hawniiﾉ擁 e cuﾉ熔rgol kaﾅ暁菊 e koﾉ容 hittuﾉ容, maa conci satta-cogguuji,
\v 10 kono ko waﾉ蓉gol kuuﾉ容 moﾆｴﾆｴe, hara ko yaaduﾉ容 e kuuﾉ容 rewﾉ兎 qirritiiﾉ兎 rewugol Alla.
\p 
\v 11 Awa kadi yo debbo jangu e nder deeﾆｴere e yankinaare timmunde.
\v 12 Mi yamiraali non debbo jannugol, maa laamagol gorko, kono ko yo o deeﾆｴu.
\v 13 Ko fii ko *Aadama adaa tageede, si *Hawaa hikki ﾉ熔n.
\v 14 Awa kadi wonaa Aadama ﾉ預ynanoo, kono ko debbo on ﾉ預ynanoo, o bonni yamiroore Alla nden.
\v 15 Kono fow e mun, debbo dandirte jiidi mun ndin si o duumike e nder gomﾉ擁nal ngal e giggol e laaﾉ殿l no haaniri.
\c 3
\s1 Fii no Ardotooﾉ兎 e Wallitotooﾉ兎 Moftal ngal Haani Wonirde
\p 
\v 1 No wi'aa: on mo no yelii wonugol yeesoojo ka *moftal Alla, haray ontigi ko huunde moﾆｴﾆｴere woni ko faalaa. Ngol kongol ko haqiiqawol.
\v 2 Kono fow e mun yo taw ardotooﾉ熔 on ko neﾉ遼熔 mo felnaaki, hara ko yondinorﾉ熔 debbo gooto, waawuﾉ熔 hoore mun, hara wonaa uﾉ橡妬toowo, hara ko o teddintooﾉ熔, wernoowo hoﾉ橡兎, waawuﾉ熔 jannude,
\v 3 hara hinaa yaroowo mandila, hinaa ﾉｲaaﾉ蓉ﾉ熔, kono hara ko o newiiﾉ熔, hara hinaa yeddondirteeﾉ熔, hara ko mo haajaaka e ngaluuji aduna,
\v 4 hara ko ardotooﾉ熔 moﾆｴﾆｴa ﾉ兎ynguure mun nden tigi, e ne'uﾉ熔 fayﾉ兎 mun ﾉ兎n, hara hiﾉ兎 yankinanii mo e nder teddungal timmungal.
\v 5 Ko fii si goﾉ遼熔 waawataa ardaade ﾉ兎ynguure mun nden tigi, haray ko honno ontigi waawata dankorde moftal Alla ngal?
\v 6 Yo taw wonaa gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 kesun, fii wota o heewu townitaare, haa o yana e ﾉｲaawoore nde Ibuliisa ﾉｲaawaa nden.
\v 7 Bee o heﾉ妬ra ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁naa ﾉ兎n kadi seeditoore moﾆｴﾆｴere, fii wota o heﾉ砥 feloore, o yana e pircol Ibuliisa.
\p 
\v 8 Wallitotooﾉ兎 moftal ngal ﾉ兎n kadi wano non, hiﾉ兎 haani wonude tedduﾉ兎, woﾉ遼擁tiiﾉ兎 faasiqiyaagal e njaram feﾆｴﾆｴituﾉ預n e ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬rgol miile.
\v 9 Hiﾉ兎 haani humaade e goonga lugguﾉ熔 gomﾉ擁nal ngal e nder ﾉ兎rnde laaﾉ砥nde.
\v 10 Kamﾉ兎 kadi non hiﾉ兎 haanaa ndarndeede taho, onsay non si tawii hay huunde alaa ko ﾉ兎 feliree, ﾉ兎 waﾉ預 non ﾉ容n golle.
\p 
\v 11 Rewﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kadi wano non, yo ﾉ兎 wonu tedduﾉ兎, hara ﾉ兎 wonaali ﾉｲo'ooﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 wona waawuﾉ兎 hoore maﾉ橡兎 e sella-findeeﾉ兎 e kala huunde.
\p 
\v 12 Wallitotooﾉ熔 on no haani tawde ko yondinorﾉ熔 debbo gooto, e ne'irﾉ熔 ﾉ妬ﾉ橡兎 mun ﾉ兎n e ﾉ兎ynguure mun nden no moﾆｴﾆｴiri.
\v 13 Ko fii kala wallitotooﾉ熔, golluﾉ熔 ﾉ容n golle no moﾆｴﾆｴiri, heﾉ登yay teddungal tiiﾉ蓉ngal e hoolaare mawnde ka gomﾉ擁ngol makko Iisaa Almasiihu on.
\p 
\v 14 Mi windanii ma ﾉ蓉nﾉ熔o e hoore tanﾆｴinagol mi yahay ka maa ko neeﾉ殿a.
\v 15 Kono si mi aru e tongaade, ﾉ蓉n a anday ko honno haanuﾉ預a wuurirde ka suudu Alla, ndun-le ko moftal Alla Wuuruﾉ熔 on, doosal e ﾉ殿lal goonga on.
\v 16 Awa kadi no fellitaa wonde gundoo ngal dewal no mawni:
\q1 ﾂｫﾆ隔n ko on feeﾉｲirﾉ熔 ﾉ殿ndu,
\q1 holliraaﾉ熔 Ruuhu Alla ko o feewuﾉ熔,
\q1 feeﾉｲanﾉ熔 malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n,
\q1 on jantaaﾉ熔 fii mun e hakkunde leﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁n,
\q1 o gomﾉ擁naa e nder aduna on,
\q1 o ﾆｴentinaa ka kammu e nder mangural.ﾂｻ
\c 4
\s1 Fii Yamirooje ﾉ容 Timotee Yamiraa ﾉ容n
\p 
\v 1 Kono Ruuhu Allaahu on no holli no laaﾉ妬ri wonde, ka saa'iiji sakkitori woﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n tertoyto gomﾉ擁nal ngal fii jokkugol ruuhuuji ﾉ預ynayﾉ擁 e janndeeji jinna,
\v 2 ﾉ兎 ﾉ預yniree faasiqankaaku e waajuuji fenaandeeji, tawa ﾉ兎rnde maﾉ橡兎 nden no jukkiniraa wa ko sunniraa njanﾉ容 wojjiniraaﾉ容 yiite.
\v 3 ﾆ‘n yimﾉ兎 wi'oyay wota dese waﾉ蓉, ﾉ兎 harmina ﾉｲaameteeji ﾉ擁 Alla waﾉ擁 fii yo gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e anduﾉ兎 goonga on ﾉ兎n ﾉｲaamu e nder jarnugol mo ﾉ擁n.
\v 4 Hara-le ko Alla tagi kon fow no moﾆｴﾆｴi, huunde wonaa ko bugitetee. Ko jarnugol tun Alla nde hiﾉ容n huutora.
\v 5 Ko fii ko Alla tagi kon fow no *laﾉ橡妬niraa daaluyee on e toraare.
\p 
\v 6 Si a weeﾉ妬tanii ﾉ蓉n musiﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, a wonanay Iisaa Almasiihu on kurkaadu moﾆｴﾆｴuru, eltiraaﾉ熔 daaluyeeji gomﾉ擁nal ngal wondude e janndeeji moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁 jokkuﾉ預a ﾉ擁n tigi.
\v 7 Kono an, bugito taali neﾉ遼預nke mehi ﾉ擁 yummiraaﾉ兎 yewtata. Eltiraa hoore maa wuurirgol wano Alla faaliraa non.
\v 8 Ko fii eltugol ﾉ殿ndu ndun ko seeﾉ預 nafi, kono wuurirgol wano Alla faaliraa non kan no wondi e nafa e nooneeji ﾉ擁n fow, no wondi kadi e fodaari ngurndan fewndiiﾉ預n ﾉ預n e aroyayﾉ預n ﾉ預n.
\v 9 Ngol ko kongol haqiiqawol, handungol e jaﾉ兎ede few wano ngol woniri non.
\v 10 Ko wonﾉ容n gollirde tippira, ko fii en waﾉ擁i tama'u men on e Alla Wuuruﾉ熔 on, on Dandoowo yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fow, tentinii gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n.
\p 
\v 11 E hino ko haanuﾉ預a yamirde, janna kon.
\v 12 Wota hay gooto yawo ma fii ko a suka, kono wonan gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n misal e kongol e jikku e giggol e gomﾉ擁nal e laaﾉ殿l.
\v 13 ﾆ覚o e mi arude, cato e jangangol yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n daaluyee on, waajoﾉ預a ﾉ兎, jannaa ﾉ兎.
\v 14 Wota a weddito e dokkal maa ngal, ngal yeﾉ擁ranoﾉ預a *hiitaango ngal, fewndo ko ardotooﾉ兎 *moftal ngal *fawi juuﾉ容 e hoore maa.
\v 15 Huutor, wonaa e ﾉ蓉n tun, fii no golle maa ﾉ容n ﾉ殿ngirana fow.
\v 16 Wattaa yiila e hoore maa e ko jannataa kon e nder cataare. Ko fii si a waﾉ擁rii non, a danday hoore maa, dandaa heﾉ熔tooﾉ兎 ma ﾉ兎n.
\c 5
\s1 Fii no Gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Haani Wondirde
\p 
\v 1 Awa kadi wota a felir nayeejo no sattiri, kono waajor mo wa si ko o ben maa, sukaaﾉ兎 worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kadi wa miﾉｲﾉｲiraaﾉ兎 maa,
\v 2 rewﾉ兎 nayeeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kadi wa neeniraaﾉ兎 maa, jiwﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kadi wa bandiraaﾉ兎 maa e nder laaﾉ殿l timmungal.
\p 
\v 3 Teddinaa kadi keynguuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, hara ko keynguuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 alaa ballo ﾉ兎n.
\v 4 Si keynguujo no mari ﾉ妬ﾉ橡兎 maa taaniraaﾉ兎, yo ﾉ兎n ekkito taho wuurirgol wano Alla faaliraa non e telen-ma ﾉ預nkagol ﾉ兎ynguure maﾉ橡兎 nden tigi, ko nii ﾉ兎 yoﾉ妬tirta mawﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, ko fii ﾉ蓉n no wela Alla.
\v 5 Keynguujo tigi-tigiijo mo alaa ballo on no waﾉ擁 tama'u mun on e Alla, duumii e toragol mo jemma e ﾉｲalorma.
\v 6 Kono keynguujo jokkuﾉ熔 mbeleeﾉ容 ko mayﾉ熔, fii kala himo wuuri.
\v 7 Ko ﾉ蓉nﾉ熔o haanuﾉ預a waajaade fii wota ﾉ兎n keynguuﾉ兎 wonu felniiﾉ兎.
\v 8 On mo dankaaki siﾉ橡兎 mun ﾉ兎n, tentinii ﾉ兎ynguure mun nden, haray o bugitike gomﾉ擁nal ngal, awa kadi haray hay mo gomﾉ擁naa no ﾉ砥ri mo.
\p 
\v 9 Fii yo keynguujo windodu e keynguuﾉ兎 haanaaﾉ兎 walliteede ﾉ兎n, yo taw ko fanﾉ擁 woo himo mari duuﾉ妬 cappanﾉ容 jeegoo, hara kadi ko yondinornooﾉ熔 gorko gooto,
\v 10 hara kadi ko andiraaﾉ熔 kuuﾉ容 moﾆｴﾆｴe, wano ne'ugol fayﾉ兎, wernugol kadi hoﾉ橡兎, sembugol koyﾉ容 yimﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎n, wallitagol tampuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, waﾉ蓉gol kala kuugal moﾆｴﾆｴal.
\p 
\v 11 Kono wota a jaﾉ砥 winditude keynguuﾉ兎 hecciﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ko fii nde himmeeji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n woﾉ遼擁ntini ﾉ兎 *Almasiihu on woo, ﾉ兎 faalete ﾆｴetteede,
\v 12 ﾉ兎 adda ﾉｲaawoore Alla e hoore maﾉ橡兎, sabu ko ﾉ兎 firti *ahadi maﾉ橡兎 araniri ndin kon.
\v 13 E hoore ﾉ蓉n, ﾉ兎 wona puyﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 wowtinoo naata e nduu, yalta e nduu, ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎yda e ﾉ蓉n ﾉｲooreeji, ﾉ兎 wona humpaaﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 wona e wowlugol piiji ﾉ擁 haanaaka wowleede.
\v 14 Ko ﾉ蓉n waﾉ擁 si mi wi'i yo keynguuﾉ兎 hecciﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾆｴette, ﾉ兎 heﾉ殿 ﾉ妬ﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 ardoo ﾉ兎ynguure maﾉ橡兎 nden, fii wota en jonnu liddotooﾉ兎 en ﾉ兎n jolkun woo no ﾉ兎 aybinira en.
\v 15 Ko fii wuren woﾉ橡兎 e maﾉ橡兎 murtii, jokkii Ibuliisa.
\p 
\v 16 Si debbo gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 no mari keynguuﾉ兎 ka mun, yo o wallito ﾉ兎, hara hinaa *moftal ngal fawtii ﾉ兎, fii no moftal ngal waawira wallitorde keynguuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 alaa ballo ﾉ兎n.
\p 
\v 17 Ardotooﾉ兎 moftal ngal moﾆｴﾆｴa no handi e teddungal sowondirngal, tentinii ﾉ兎n wakkiliiﾉ兎 yangi waajagol e jannugol.
\v 18 Ko fii bindi ﾉ擁n no wi'i: ﾂｫWota mo buuma hunduko ngaari ndin nde hindi yaaﾉ殿na ﾉ蓉n maaroﾂｻ, awa kadi: ﾂｫGolloowo no handi e njoddi mun.ﾂｻ
\v 19 Wota a jaﾉ砥 tooﾉｲe e hoore ardotooﾉ熔 woo, si hinaa a heﾉ砥 seeditiiﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔 maa tato.
\v 20 Duumiiﾉ兎 e waﾉ蓉gol junuubu ﾉ兎n, wurtu ﾉ兎 e yeeso fow, fii no heddiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kadi hulira.
\p 
\v 21 E yeeso Alla e Iisaa Almasiihu on e malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 suﾉ殿aﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, mi yamirii ma jokkugol ﾉ容e yamirooje e ﾉ殿awo ﾉ砥rdindingol maa giﾉ預ale.
\p 
\v 22 Wota a hawju *fawugol juuﾉ容 e hoore hay gooto toﾉ遼熔o mo fii golle Alla ﾉ容n. Wota a tawde e junuubaaji woﾉ橡兎. Reeno, wonaa laaﾉ砥ﾉ熔.
\p 
\v 23 Accu yarugol ndiyan tun, huutoraa kadi njaram *wiiﾉｲu seeﾉ預, sabu nawnahoy reedu maa jokkondirkoy koy.
\p 
\v 24 Junuubaaji yimﾉ兎 goo no feeﾉｲi ado ﾉ兎 ﾉｲaaweede, woﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n non ﾉ擁 feeﾉｲirii woo yeeso.
\v 25 Ko wano non kadi kuuﾉ容 moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n no feeﾉｲi, hay ﾉ容 feeﾉｲaa ﾉ容n kadi waawataa suuﾉ預ade.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Yo jiyaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fow jogor jeyﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉n ﾉ兎n wa handuﾉ兎 e teddungal timmungal, fii wota innde Alla nden e jannde nden hoyne.
\v 2 ﾆ‘n jiyaaﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 tawata jeyﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉n ﾉ兎n ko gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 haanaa ka ﾉ兎 ronka ﾉ兎 teddinde, ﾉ殿y ﾉ兎n ko musiﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎. Kono hiﾉ兎 haani ﾉ砥rtude kurkanaade ﾉ兎, ko fii ﾉ兎n wonﾉ兎 nafitorde golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, ko yiﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎. Ko ﾉ蓉n haanuﾉ預a jannude waajoo.
\s1 Fii Jandeeji Bonﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n e Giggol Kaalisi
\p 
\v 3 Si goﾉ遼熔 no jannirde noone goo, hara o alaa jokkude konguﾉ擁 selluﾉ擁 Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on, e janndeeji yaaduﾉ擁 e laawol Alla ngol,
\v 4 haray on ko townitiiﾉ熔, mo andaa huunde, wonduﾉ熔 e nawnaare yeddondiral e pooﾉ熔tiro haala. Ko ﾉ蓉n wonata neene nawliigu e pooﾉ熔tiro e hoyre e sikkitaareeji bonﾉ擁,
\v 5 e yeddondire ﾉ容 lannataa hakkunde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 hakkille bonﾉ容, ﾉ兎 andaa goonga, jogorﾉ兎 dewal ngal wa ﾉ砥ndu keﾉ殿l.
\p 
\v 6 Ko goonga, dewal ngal ko tono moolanaaﾉ熔, si tawii en yondinorii ko jogiﾉ容n kon.
\v 7 Ko fii en addoraano hay huunde e oo aduna, awa kadi en nattortaa hay huunde.
\v 8 Si tawii non hiﾉ容n mari neema e conci, yo ﾉ蓉n yonu en.
\v 9 Kono ﾉ兎n faalaaﾉ兎 alﾉ蓉de yanay e nder jarrabuyee, e nder pircol, e faaleeji ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ擁 njofooji, bonnayﾉ擁, ko yollata yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e nder yeebaare e halkaare.
\v 10 Ko fii giggol kaalisi ko ﾉ預ﾉ熔l kala bone. E nder ko woﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n himmani ﾉ蓉n kon, ﾉ兎 woﾉ遼擁tii gomﾉ擁nal ngal, ﾉ兎 waﾉ擁tii kamﾉ兎 tigi tampereeji.
\s1 Fii Yamirooje ﾉ容 Timotee Yamiraa ﾉ容n
\p 
\v 11 An non, oo aaden Alla, dogu ﾉ擁n piiji, ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬taa peewal ngal e wuurirgol no Alla faaliraa non e gomﾉ擁nal ngal e giggol ngol e wakkilaare nden e newaare nden.
\v 12 Tippiraa tippiro moﾆｴﾆｴo fii gomﾉ擁nal ngal, catoﾉ預a e *ngurndan poomayankejan ﾉ預n, ﾉ預n noddiraﾉ預a fii mun ﾉ預n, ﾉ預n qirritorﾉ預a qirritannde moﾆｴﾆｴere fii mun yeeso seedeeﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ兎.
\v 13 Mi yamirii ma e yeeso Alla, on Yeﾉ熔owo ngurndan kala huunde, e yeeso Iisaa Almasiihu on, on seeditorﾉ熔 qirritannde mun moﾆｴﾆｴere nden yeeso Pilaatu Pontii lanﾉ熔 on,
\v 14 ﾉ熔fto yamiroore nden e hoore laaﾉ殿l e no felnoraa, haa nde Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on feeﾉｲi.
\v 15 Feeﾉｲugol makko laatoo e saa'i mo Alla happi on, ﾉ蓉n ko on Yeesoojo bajjo moﾆｴﾆｴo, Lanﾉ熔 lamﾉ兎, Koohoojo koohooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n,
\v 16 on mo tawata ko kaﾉｲun tun woni maayataa, Hoﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 e jalbeendi ndi ﾉ殿dotaako, mo goﾉ遼熔 woo yi'aali, waawataa yi'ude kadi, on mo teddungal e bawgal wonani haa poomaa. Aamiina!
\p 
\v 17 Yamir alﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e oo aduna fewndiiﾉ熔, wota ﾉ兎 wonu mawnintiniiﾉ兎, wota ﾉ兎 faw tama'u maﾉ橡兎 on e ngaluuji ﾉ擁 luttataa ﾉ擁n, kono yo ﾉ兎 waﾉ蓉 tama'u maﾉ橡兎 e Alla, on Yeﾉ熔owo en fow haa feﾆｴﾆｴita fii no weltoroyoﾉ容n.
\v 18 Yo ﾉ兎 waﾉ蓉 ko moﾆｴﾆｴi, ﾉ兎 alﾉ擁ra kuuﾉ容 moﾆｴﾆｴe, ﾉ兎 wona okkooﾉ兎 e kafidotooﾉ兎.
\v 19 Waﾉ蓉gol maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ蓉n, ko wa sincugol didol moﾆｴﾆｴol fii ko aroyta kon, e fii no ﾉ兎 tamira ngurndan haqiiqajan ﾉ預n.
\p 
\v 20 Ko an yo Timotee, jogito koo ko halfinaﾉ預a, e nder reenagol e haalaaji mehi, ﾉ擁 yaadaa e faale Alla on, e yeddondire fii gandal fenaandewal,
\v 21 e nder ko woﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n humii e ngal gandal kon, ﾉ兎 seli gomﾉ擁nal ngal.
\p Yo moﾆｴﾆｴere Joomiraaﾉ熔 on wonu e mon!
